sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant L as Eng Lead
    participant C as Coordinator
    participant S as Security
    participant P as Product

    L->>C: deliberate.open<br/>rule = weighted_vote_with_veto:2.0<br/>veto: Security
    C->>S: dispatch (notification)
    C->>P: dispatch (notification)
    S->>C: deliberate.comment<br/>(context: maintenance window)
    L->>C: deliberate.comment<br/>(context: pre-approval)
    P->>C: deliberate.comment<br/>(context: customer impact)
    L->>C: deliberate.vote (yea, 1.0)
    P->>C: deliberate.vote (yea, 1.0)
    S->>C: deliberate.vote (yea, 1.0, veto_invoked=false)
    L->>C: deliberate.close
    C-->>L: outcome = approved<br/>tally yea=3.0
    C->>P: notify (decision artefact id)
    C->>S: notify (decision artefact id)
    Note over C: All exchanges appended<br/>to evidence chain;<br/>decision artefact produced.
